cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is about visual captioning, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of language models, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper investigates the performance of different models, which is related to machine learning and could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the difficulty of different datasets, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
